+# CVE-2026-42216 — Not Applicable to Debian Bullseye `openexr` (2.5.4)
+
+## Summary
+
+CVE-2026-42216 fixes out-of-bounds reads when expanding IDManifest
+prefix-compressed strings in OpenEXR. The vulnerable code lives entirely in
+the IDManifest attribute implementation (`ImfIDManifest.cpp`, `ImfIDManifest.h`,
+and related attribute helpers) introduced **after** OpenEXR 2.5.4.
+
+Debian bullseye ships **openexr 2.5.4-2+deb11u1**, which predates the
+IDManifest feature. There is no source location to which the upstream fix can
+be backported; the package is **not vulnerable**.
+
+## Upstream fixes (3.x only)
+
+- PR #2377 / commit 296bef0d — Fix OOB read when expanding IDManifest
+  prefix-compressed strings
+- PR #2378 / commit 21eaa33b — Harden IDManifest parsing against illegal
+  shift and string prefix OOB
+
+## Verification against openexr 2.5.4
+
+- `find . -iname '*IDManifest*'` returns no matches
+- Grep for `IDManifest`, `idManifest`, and `readVariableLengthInteger` across
+  all `.cpp`/`.h` files returns no matches
+- `configure.ac` reports `AC_INIT(OpenEXR, 2.5.4)`
+
+## Affected versions (per CVE record)
+
+The IDManifest feature was introduced in upstream commit c61ddf2725e7, which
+first appears in the **3.0.0** release line. OpenEXR **2.5.4** is below that
+floor and is outside the published affected ranges for this CVE.
+
+| Distro | Release  | Package | Source version      | Status           |
+| ------ | -------- | ------- | ------------------- | ---------------- |
+| Debian | Bullseye | openexr | 2.5.4-2+deb11u1     | **Not affected** |
+
+## Recommendation
+
+Mark CVE-2026-42216 as **not-affected** / **not-applicable** for the openexr
+source package in Debian bullseye (and any other distribution still on the
+2.5.x branch that predates the IDManifest feature).
+
+## References
+
+- https://github.com/AcademySoftwareFoundation/openexr/pull/2377
+- https://github.com/AcademySoftwareFoundation/openexr/pull/2378
+- https://github.com/AcademySoftwareFoundation/openexr/commit/296bef0d165ea83162f720827d6f5e86d7f9f3a6
+- https://github.com/AcademySoftwareFoundation/openexr/commit/21eaa33bcbbb0c83a5fc42f6b6d65b70a996e63c
