+| CVE | CVE-2026-34543 |
+| Package | openexr / libopenexr25 / libopenexr-dev |
+| Installed version | 2.5.4-2+deb11u1 |
+| Affected range | 3.4.0 – 3.4.7 |
+| Assessment | **NOT AFFECTED** — version below lower bound; vulnerable files absent; legacy C++ decoder uses correct `tmpSize` bounds check |
+| Action required | None. Mark as false positive / not affected in scanner. |
+| Evidence | `src/lib/OpenEXRCore/` does not exist in 2.5.4. PXR24 decoding lives in `OpenEXR/IlmImf/ImfPxr24Compressor.cpp` and bounds-checks against `tmpSize` (actual zlib output length). |
+
